,"focus":"1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"那老哥什么时候回来？","id":15,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"总裁现在应当正在前往圣山的路上，过两天就能回来了。","id":17,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我只是想去散步也不行吗？","id":19,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_267_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"只是在宅子附近的话......我会派人跟着你。","id":21,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩希亚，现在谢拉格的形势十分险峻，这也是为了你好。","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_267_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......唉。","id":24,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"character","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"character","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":30},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_bg_24_g8_nobleroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":31},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"老哥......你就一定要这么做吗？","id":34,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"博士，我该怎么办......","id":36,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"character","id":38},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"5","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":41},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"极光？！","id":43,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"嘘——好严密的守备，我好不容易才进来的。","id":45,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"你不是和Sharp队长一起去博士那边了吗？","id":47,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"嗯，我这次来，就是博士有话要我带给你。","id":49,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":51},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"character","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e7/Avg_bg_24_g12_mountpath.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":56},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":57,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"你确定？","id":60,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫希","text":"是的，阿克托斯在领地内集结了大量士兵，但是，这支队伍的领导者是那位博士，而不是阿克托斯。","id":62,"figure":["avg_npc_255_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"阿克托斯人呢？","id":64,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫希","text":"不清楚......根据眼线的回报，在将这支队伍的指挥权正式交给博士后，他就不知所踪了。","id":66,"figure":["avg_npc_255_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"......那个博士的队伍是诱饵？不，不会这么简单。","id":68,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"规模呢？","id":69,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫希","text":"佩尔罗契领地响应阿克托斯号召的家族和您想象的差不多，以此估算的话——阿克托斯应该不可能再集结起另外一支同样规模的队伍。","id":71,"figure":["avg_npc_255_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"但是他不可能待在后方，有另一支队伍的可能性很大。","id":73,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫希","text":"佩尔罗契家的战士本来就很擅长在山野中行动，这确实不是没有可能。","id":75,"figure":["avg_npc_255_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"但是，无论是诱饵还是主力，这支队伍都不能放任不理。","id":77,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"让魏斯传令，命战士们在山下集结，等候命令。","id":78,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"然后派人去盯着大部队，你主要负责去找出阿克托斯的踪迹。","id":79,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_255_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫希","text":"是。","id":81,"figure":["avg_npc_255_1",5]},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"character","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":88},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_bg_24_g8_nobleroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":89},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":90},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"博士......希望我能登上圣山，潜入蔓珠院去找姐姐？","id":93,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"是的。","id":95,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"博士的意思是，如今，佩尔罗契家和希瓦艾什家之间的冲突已经几乎无法避免了。","id":96,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是，如果说还有一个人可以阻止这一切的话，那么，这个人必然是你的姐姐，当代圣女，恩雅·希瓦艾什。","id":97,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"但是......","id":99,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"原本，博士是想秉承罗德岛不干政的方针，选择袖手旁观的。","id":101,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是，博士指出一点，既然还政对于恩希欧迪斯先生来说只是一个幌子，那么他也必然不会将对谢拉格的信仰放在眼中。","id":102,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"而一旦希瓦艾什家的部队真的击败了佩尔罗契家的部队，那么对他来说，阻拦他将谢拉格纳入囊中的，也就只有蔓珠院。","id":103,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"也就是谢拉格人民的信仰对象，圣女。","id":104,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"博士说，他并不是想要让你去说服圣女做些什么，而是你曾经拜托过他，希望他能够帮忙缓和你们兄妹之间关系。","id":106,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"他对于自己来到谢拉格后没有帮上忙一直感到有些自责。","id":107,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"这怎么能怪博士！我才要对博士和随行的各位道歉，明明应该是一次愉快的旅行，结果却因为老哥而变成了这个样子......","id":109,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"这也不怪你呀，崖心。","id":111,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"总之，博士的意思是，他可以不在乎很多东西，但一方面他从一开始就被恩希欧迪斯先生卷了进来。","id":112,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"另一方面，你是恩希欧迪斯先生的妹妹也是不争的事实。","id":113,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"所以，博士还是打算做一些什么。","id":114,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"让你上山，是希望你能成为圣女身边的保险。","id":115,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"博士希望我在必要的时候去阻止老哥。","id":117,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"或者在必要的时候带着圣女逃跑。","id":119,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......","id":121,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":122},{"type":"character","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"恩希亚下意识地摸了摸自己手中的绳环。","id":124},{"type":"text","text":"这是小时候，姐姐亲手为她编织的。","id":125},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#2$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......","id":128,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我去。","id":132,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"这是一次潜入行动，我和其他的随行干员会一起协助你。","id":134,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......不。","id":136,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我有更好的办法。","id":137,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"大家只要能帮我到达圣山脚下就好，剩下的，交给我一个人。","id":139,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"character","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":145},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e7/Avg_bg_24_g12_mountpath.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":146},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":147,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormflp","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#3$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"博士，为什么你要把行军的速度控制得这么慢？","id":151,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#3$1","focus":"-1","id":153},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"155","text":"要让观察着我们的眼睛再多欣赏欣赏。"},"2":{"id":"155","text":"现在还不能快。"}},"values":[],"id":154},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":155,"end":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"我说，古罗你该不会还没搞清楚我们要干什么吧？","id":157,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#1$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"不就是吸引希瓦艾什家的注意吗？我就是觉得有点太慢了。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"我看你就是想直接冲过去和希瓦艾什家打一仗。","id":161,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#2$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"那当然。","id":163,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"之前被瓦莱丝压了一头，我现在胸口憋着一口气呢。","id":164,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",1],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"character","id":166},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowbootwalk","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_284_1$1","fadetime":"1","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩尔罗契家战士","text":"博士，在大典上被抓走的尤卡坦的位置确认了。","id":170,"figure":["avg_npc_284_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"佩尔罗契家战士","text":"和您想的一样，没有被带回希瓦艾什家的领地，而是就近关在了山脚下的镇子里。","id":171,"figure":["avg_npc_284_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_284_1$1","focus":"-1","id":173},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"175","text":"辛苦了。"}},"values":[],"id":174},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":175,"end":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#4$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"博士，你可真厉害啊，这么短的时间里就能摸清楚尤卡坦老爷被关押的位置。","id":177,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"哼，这点情报收集，我布朗陶家的人也做得到。","id":179,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#3$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"总之，既然确认了尤卡坦的位置，我和这个傻大个也该动起来了吧？","id":181,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",2],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":182},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#3$1","focus":"-1","id":183},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"185","text":"是的。"}},"values":[],"id":184},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":185,"end":209},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#5$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"......","id":187,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#10$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"你沉默什么？","id":189,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#6$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"什么，原来你在喊我吗？我可不是傻大个！","id":191,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#7$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"（深呼吸）","id":193,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#8$1","id":194},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"古罗！将军！哼......这样就行了吧？","id":196,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"我问你，你知道你要做什么吧？","id":197,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#4$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"我知道，去最近的车站搞点破坏，让你有机会去救你丈夫。","id":199,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"知道就好。","id":201,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"替博士警告你一句，别真的搞出人命来。","id":202,"figure":["avg_npc_262_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#2$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"哼，车站里都是些平民百姓，我古罗是绝不会对他们出手的。","id":204,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#7$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"不过，博士，要是希瓦艾什家的人真来了——","id":206,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_260_1#1$1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古罗","text":"我只能说，我会尽量留手。","id":208,"figure":["avg_npc_260_1",0]},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":209,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":211},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"character","id":214},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":215},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_bg_24_g10_manorhouse.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":216},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":217,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#8$1","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"崖心，你说你要找的......是你的登山设备？","id":220,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"没错。","id":222,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"难道说，你要攀登喀兰圣山？","id":224,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"嗯......按照你说的，现在别说圣山上，圣山下肯定也有很多人了。","id":226,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"如果要从正面上圣山，就算是Sharp队长大概也很难潜进去。","id":227,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"不过这可难不倒我~","id":229,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"只要能到达山脚下，剩下的交给我就好。","id":230,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是......这样的话，我和其他人就不能保护你了。","id":232,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"没事没事。","id":234,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我也在罗德岛接受过许多训练，一般的对手我还是应付得过来的。","id":235,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"可......","id":237,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"character","id":239},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":240},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":241},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_275","fadetime":"1","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":244},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#4$1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩希亚，你要去哪？","id":246,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"切斯特叔叔......","id":248,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我想要去登山。","id":249,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#5$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"你要去登哪座山？","id":251,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"喀兰圣山。","id":253,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#2$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"那里即将成为战场，你过去会受伤的。","id":255,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"你要去那里干什么？","id":256,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......","id":258,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"切斯特叔叔，自从我爱上登山之后，我就一直想要用自己的双手爬上喀兰圣山看看。","id":259,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"自从姐姐成为圣女离我们而去之后，这想法就越来越强烈......总有一天，我要爬上它的顶峰，把姐姐接回家。","id":260,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"而现在，这个机会来了。","id":262,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#2$1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"你做不到的，恩希亚。","id":264,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......即使我做不到把姐姐带回家，至少在这个时候，我也要陪在姐姐身边。","id":266,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"老哥做了这么多的事，姐姐一定也很迷茫。","id":267,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#9$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"我没有办法阻止老哥，那么，至少，我要陪在姐姐的身边！","id":269,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#3$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"......","id":271,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":273},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":274},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":275},{"type":"text","text":"奥拉维尔，你最小的女儿，也已经长大了。","id":276},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"character","id":278},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_286_1$1","fadetime":"1","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希瓦艾什家士官","text":"二小姐，抱歉，老爷的命令是，为了您的安全着想，不允许您离开这座宅邸。","id":282,"figure":["avg_npc_286_1",0]},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":283,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"......停手吧。","id":285,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"欸。","id":287,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"切斯特叔叔！","id":288,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_286_1$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希瓦艾什家士官","text":"切斯特经理，你这是违抗老爷的命令！","id":290,"figure":["avg_npc_286_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#6$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"这里发生的事一切责任由我承担。","id":292,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_286_1$1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希瓦艾什家士官","text":"这......虽然你都这么说了，可是二小姐她的安危......","id":294,"figure":["avg_npc_286_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"希瓦艾什家的人，从来不会冒无谓的风险。","id":296,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"这里，就相信她吧。","id":297,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_286_1$1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希瓦艾什家士官","text":"这......好吧。","id":299,"figure":["avg_npc_286_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"去吧，为二小姐和几位罗德岛的客人准备最好的驮兽。","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_286_1$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希瓦艾什家士官","text":"我知道了。","id":303,"figure":["avg_npc_286_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"谢谢你，切斯特叔叔！","id":305,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"谢谢您，切斯特经理。","id":307,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我一直以为您......","id":308,"figure":["avg_422_aurora_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#7$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"不必谢我。","id":310,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"去吧，时间紧迫。","id":311,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"嗯！","id":313,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩希亚。","id":315,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"嗯？","id":317,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#7$1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"注意安全。","id":319,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"......好！","id":321,"figure":["avgnew_173_slchan_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":322},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":323},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":324},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#1$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"奥拉维尔。","id":327,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#3$1","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"在你和伊丽莎白死后，我一直后悔，过去应该支持你对领地的改革，而不是与你作对。","id":329,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"所以，当你儿子想要继承你的理想时，我选择了毫无保留地支持他。","id":330,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩希欧迪斯他做得很好。","id":331,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩雅作为圣女也得到了谢拉格人的爱戴。","id":332,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"恩希亚虽然得了矿石病，但她的病情得到了抑制，而且一如既往地开朗。","id":333,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_267_1#6$1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"切斯特","text":"只是，我刚才忽然反应过来。","id":335,"figure":["avg_npc_267_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":336},{"type":"character","id":337},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"我有多久没有见到这三个孩子聚在一起，露出兄妹之间应有的笑容了呢？","id":339},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"character","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":345},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":346},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_24_g3_mainhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":348},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_sjoyasorrow_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":349,"musicid":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":350},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"......","id":352,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"character","id":354},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":355},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":356},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"大长老，您应当好好休息......","id":359,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"......","id":361,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"按照记录，这座大殿，是在三族议会成立后，三族的人民共同建造的。三族人民的存在与合作要远远早于现代三族制度的建立。","id":362,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"在那之后，过了上千年，中间修修补补，最终成了现在的样子。","id":363,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"而这张椅子，也在这里摆了上千年。","id":364,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"有十几位大长老坐在这张椅子上面，度过了他们的一生。","id":365,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"......就好像，有十几位圣女，都在这座山上郁郁而终。","id":367,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"从一开始，圣女就是蔓珠院为了方便信仰传播而捏造出来的。","id":369,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#7$1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"大长老在这个时候提及我早就知道的事实，难道是想说，信仰是虚假的？","id":371,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"你的话也直接起来了，但事情恰恰相反，恩雅，不，圣女。","id":373,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"圣女，咳咳，你知道老朽的名字吗？","id":374,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#10$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"......不知道。","id":376,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"这座蔓珠院中，恐怕已经没人记得了。","id":378,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"就连老朽自己，都已经忘了。","id":379,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"每一任的大长老，在接过上一任的衣钵之后，都会只成为大长老。","id":380,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"将来，人们也会忘记你的名字，只知道你叫作圣女。","id":381,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"然后，大长老和圣女都会发现——","id":382,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们信仰的，并非耶拉冈德。","id":384,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们可以信仰任何东西，只要一个故事，一些巧合，他们就会信仰你，信仰我，信仰恩希欧迪斯，信仰山，信仰水，甚至信仰一片树叶。","id":385,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"既然人们什么都可以信仰，那么信仰究竟是什么？","id":386,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"大长老们最终得出了答案：","id":387,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们信仰的，是信仰本身。","id":388,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#2$1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们将选择权交给信仰的对象。","id":390,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们将自己排斥的事物统统归咎于信仰。","id":391,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们无条件地信任着信仰所指导的生活方式。","id":392,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"所以信仰是什么？","id":393,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#4$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"信仰是懒惰，是逃避，是颓废！信仰是安定，信仰是停滞！咳咳咳咳咳——","id":395,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"......您该休息了，大长老。","id":397,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#4$1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"不，圣女，圣女！","id":399,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"character","id":401},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":402},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":403},{"type":"text","text":"大长老倏地抓住恩雅的手腕。","id":404},{"type":"text","text":"力道之大，在恩雅的皮肤上都留下了红印，仿佛把他毕生的力量都用在了这上面。","id":405},{"type":"text","text":"他的双眼盯着眼前的圣女，却仿佛在看着别人。","id":406},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$stranger_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_bat_stranger_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":407,"musicid":6},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#6$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"信仰丑恶！但即使如此，没有人能够摧毁信仰！","id":409,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"谢拉格历经千年，三大家族之间隔阂渐深，却无人能够否定信仰，信仰是谢拉格之所以是谢拉格的根基！","id":410,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"信仰将谢拉格人统合在了一起，人们追求信仰，人们依赖信仰！","id":411,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"谢拉格由此存在了千年！","id":412,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"人们渴望安定，人们渴望停滞！","id":413,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"恩希欧迪斯以为他赢了，他没有，他不可能赢。","id":414,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"他凭什么战胜谢拉格这千年以来凝聚而成的信仰！","id":415,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"老朽已经要不行了，但你还年轻，你是这蔓珠院的圣女，你也将成为这蔓珠院的大长老。","id":416,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"去教会他，去战胜他，让他明白，信仰面前，他的那些动作不值一提！","id":417,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"character","id":419},{"type":"text","text":"恩雅沉默片刻，却将大长老的手硬生生地从自己手腕上掰开。","id":420},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":421},{"type":"text","text":"她的眼中有着对眼前老人的怜悯，更多的，却是坚决。","id":422},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"......我不同意，大长老。","id":424,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"您说信仰意味着停滞，人们依赖信仰，是因为他们渴望安定。","id":425,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我不这么认为。","id":427,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"诚然，人一旦有所信仰，总会习惯性地依赖信仰。懒惰、逃避、颓废......您说的这些，我不否认。","id":428,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"但这绝不是说，信仰意味着停滞。","id":429,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"信仰就是信仰，信仰本身是没有属性的，信仰的内容是被赋予的。","id":430,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"信仰向前走，信仰的人也会向前走。","id":431,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"信仰停下，信仰的人也会停下。","id":432,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#9$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"谢拉格的人们之所以在您的眼中向往着停滞，正是因为对耶拉冈德的信仰在蔓珠院手中停滞了千年！","id":434,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我们遵循着某种约定俗成的规则画地为牢，在这片雪山之中生活了上千年，不去探究外面的天地，不与外面的人交流。","id":435,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"然而这种约定俗成，真的和信仰有关吗？","id":436,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"这难道不是只是蔓珠院的傲慢吗？","id":437,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#4$1","id":438},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"傲慢？不，不，它本该如此！","id":440,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#1$1","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"......没有什么事本该如此。","id":442,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"如果有，那它一定只是从未有所改变。","id":443,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"该改变了，大长老。","id":445,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_258_1#5$1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"圣女，不，你改变不了什么的。","id":447,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大长老","text":"信仰，咳咳......是谢拉格之所以是谢拉格的根基......","id":448,"figure":["avg_npc_258_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#8$1","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我会去和恩希欧迪斯对抗，但不是以您想要的方式。","id":450,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我也不知道我能不能成功。","id":451,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"但是，圣女既然从一开始就是蔓珠院用来引导民众信仰的工具。","id":452,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"那我就让这个工具真正发挥效果。","id":453,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我是圣女，但我不是蔓珠院的圣女，而是谢拉格的圣女。","id":454,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"我会用我的方式去引导人民，让他们能够自由地去前进，去探究，去冒险。","id":455,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":456},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":457},{"type":"character","name":"avg_174_slbell_1#3$1","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"而您，该休息了，大长老。","id":459,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩雅","text":"来人，将大长老扶回去。","id":460,"figure":["avg_174_slbell_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":461},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":462},{"type":"character","fadetime":"2","id":463},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":464},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":465},{"type":"text","text":"恩雅站起身，头也不回地走向正殿门外。","id":466},{"type":"dialog","id":467},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":468},{"type":"text","text":"而在她的背后，大长老坐在椅子上，注视着她的背影，他伸出手，似乎想要握住什么，最终却无力地垂下。","id":469},{"type":"text","text":"他什么也没有握住。","id":470},{"type":"text","text":"他永远地停在了那里，一如他梦中的谢拉格雪山。","id":471},{"type":"dialog","id":472},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":473},{"type":"character","id":474},{"type":"image","id":475}],"characters":["恩希亚","切斯特","极光","诺希斯","莫希","古罗","休露丝","佩尔罗契家战士","希瓦艾什家士官","大长老","恩雅"]}